            world of Illusion, only six are playable in the Core Rules, listed briefly with their mechanical funtions in the table below, or in greater detail further down on this page. 
            More races will be included in future expanded content, however, if players can't wait, they are invited to create their own races, or modify the existing ones, so long as 
